blogs.title: Habit
blogs.body:
"What is habit?"
"A way of living?"
"Tara, would you become my habit?"
blogs.author: Snow

blogs.title: Not Mine
blogs.body: The most tragic joke of my life would be, you are not mine to keep. Even if you wanted to stay back, even if I wanted to clutch you in. Somethings... are just not in our hands.
blogs.author: Snow
